.TH start-cli-backup-job-reassign-target 1  "reassign-target "
.SH NAME
start\-cli\-backup\-job\-reassign\-target \- Move an automatic backup job to another target
.SH SYNOPSIS
\fBstart\-cli backup job reassign\-target\fR [\fB\-\-wait\-for\-schedule\fR] [\fB\-\-format\fR] [\fB\-h\fR|\fB\-\-help\fR] <\fIID\fR> <\fITARGET_ID\fR> <\fIPASSWORD\fR>
.SH DESCRIPTION
Move an automatic backup job to another target
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
\fB\-\-wait\-for\-schedule\fR
Wait for the next scheduled time instead of running on the new target now
.TP
\fB\-\-format\fR

.TP
\fB\-h\fR, \fB\-\-help\fR
Print help
.TP
<\fIID\fR>
Automatic backup job identifier
.TP
<\fITARGET_ID\fR>
Backup target identifier
.TP
<\fIPASSWORD\fR>
Password for backup encryption
